#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1724
msgid "Delete holes"
msgstr "Excluir buracos"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1725
msgid ""
"Takes a polygon layer and removes holes in polygons. It creates a new vector"
" layer in which polygons with holes have been replaced by polygons with only"
" their external ring. Attributes are not modified."
msgstr ""
"Pegue a camada poligonal e remova os buracos nos polígonos. Isso cria uma "
"nova camada vetorial na qual polígonos com buracos foram substituídos por "
"polígonos com somente seu anel externo. Atributos não são modificados.  "

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1730
msgid ""
"An optional minimum area parameter allows removing only holes which are "
"smaller than a specified area threshold. Leaving this parameter at ``0.0`` "
"results in all holes being removed."
msgstr ""
"Um parâmetro de área mínima opcional permite remover somente buracos que são"
" menores que uma área especifica limitada. Deixando esse parâmetro em "
"``0.0``  resulta em todos os buracos serem removidos."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1737
msgid "Before and after the cleaning"
msgstr "Antes e depois da limpeza"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1760
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2345
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3634
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5022
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7120
msgid "Input polygon vector layer"
msgstr "insira a camada vetorial de polígonal."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1761
msgid "**Remove holes with area less than**"
msgstr "**Remover buracos com área menor que**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1764
msgid "``MIN_AREA``"
msgstr "``MIN_AREA``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1768
msgid ""
"Only holes with an area less than this threshold will be deleted. With a "
"value of ``0.0``, **all** the holes will be deleted."
msgstr ""
"Somente buracos com uma área menor que esse limite será deletada. Com o "
"valor ``0.0``, **all** os buracos serão deletados."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1771
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1794
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5377
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5400
msgid "**Cleaned**"
msgstr "**Limpo**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1797
msgid "The output (cleaned) vector layer"
msgstr "A saída (cleaned) da camada vetorial."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1802
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:deleteholes``"
msgstr "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:deleteholes`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1812
msgid "Densify by count"
msgstr "Densificar por contagem."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1813
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1899
msgid ""
"Takes a polygon or line layer and generates a new one in which the "
"geometries have a larger number of vertices than the original one."
msgstr ""
"Pega um polígono ou camada de linha e gera uma nova na qual as geometrias "
"possuem um número de vértices maior que o original."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1816
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1906
msgid ""
"If the geometries have Z or M values present then these will be linearly "
"interpolated at the added vertices."
msgstr ""
"Se as geometrias tiverem valores Z ou M presentes, eles serão interpolados "
"linearmente nos vértices adicionados."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1819
msgid ""
"The number of new vertices to add to each segment is specified as an input "
"parameter."
msgstr ""
"O número de novos vértices a serem adicionados a cada segmento é "
"especificado como um parâmetro de entrada."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1825
msgid "Red points show the vertices before and after the densify"
msgstr ""
"Os pontos vermelhos mostram os vértices antes e depois da densificação"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1833
msgid ":ref:`qgisdensifygeometriesgivenaninterval`"
msgstr ":ref:`qgisdensifygeometriesgivenaninterval`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1851
msgid "**Vertices to add**"
msgstr "**Vértices a serem adicionados**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1852
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2721
msgid "``VERTICES``"
msgstr "``VERTICES``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1855
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2173
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3217
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3639
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:4140
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:6026
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:6458
msgid "Default: 1"
msgstr "Padrão: 1"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1856
msgid "Number of vertices to add to each segment"
msgstr "Número de vértices a serem adicionados em cada segmento"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1857
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1880
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1950
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1973
msgid "**Densified**"
msgstr "**Densificado**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1883
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1976
msgid "The output (densified) vector layer"
msgstr "A saída (densificado) da camada vetorial"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1888
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:densifygeometries``"
msgstr "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:densifygeometries``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1898
msgid "Densify by interval"
msgstr "Densificar por intervalo"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1902
msgid ""
"The geometries are densified by adding regularly placed extra vertices "
"inside each segment so that the maximum distance between any two vertices "
"does not exceed the specified distance."
msgstr ""
"As geometrias são densificadas adicionando regularmente colocados vértices "
"extras dentro de cada segmento para que assim a distâncias máxima entre dois"
" vértices não exceda a distância específica."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1909
msgid "**Example**"
msgstr "**Exemplo**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1911
msgid ""
"Specifying a distance of 3 would cause the segment ``[0 0] -> [10 0]`` to be"
" converted to ``[0 0] -> [2.5 0] -> [5 0] -> [7.5 0] -> [10 0]``, since 3 "
"extra vertices are required on the segment and spacing these at 2.5 "
"increments allows them to be evenly spaced over the segment."
msgstr ""
"Especificando a distância de 3 faria com que o segmento ``[0 0] -> [10 0]`` "
"fosse convertido para  ``[0 0] -> [2.5 0] -> [5 0] -> [7.5 0] -> [10 0]``, "
"desde que 3 vértices extras sejam requeridos no segmento e espaçando estes "
"em incrementos de 2.5 permitindo-os ser uniformemente espaçados pelos "
"segmentos."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1920
msgid "Densify geometry at a given interval"
msgstr "Geometrias densificadas em um dado intervalo."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1926
msgid ":ref:`qgisdensifygeometries`"
msgstr ":ref:`qgisdensifygeometries`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1944
msgid "**Interval between vertices to add**"
msgstr "**Intervalo entre vértices a serem adicionados**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1945
msgid "``INTERVAL``"
msgstr "``INTERVAL``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1949
msgid "Maximum distance between two consecutive vertices"
msgstr "Distância máxima entre dois vértices consecutivos"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1981
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:densifygeometriesgivenaninterval``"
msgstr "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:densifygeometriesgivenaninterval``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1991
msgid "Dissolve"
msgstr "Dissolver"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1992
msgid ""
"Takes a vector layer and combines its features into new features. One or "
"more attributes can be specified to dissolve features belonging to the same "
"class (having the same value for the specified attributes), alternatively "
"all features can be dissolved to a single feature."
msgstr ""
"Pegue uma camada vetorial e combine as características em novas. Um ou mais "
"atributos podem ser especificados para dissolver características pertencendo"
" a mesma classe (tendo o mesmo valor para os atributos especificados), "
"alternativamente todas as características podem ser dissolvidas para uma "
"única característica."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1998
msgid ""
"All output geometries will be converted to multi geometries. In case the "
"input is a polygon layer, common boundaries of adjacent polygons being "
"dissolved will get erased. If enabled, the optional \"Keep disjoint features"
" separate\" setting will cause features and parts that do not overlap or "
"touch to be exported as separate features (instead of parts of a single "
"multipart feature)."
msgstr ""
"Todas as geometrias serão convertidas para geometrias múltiplas. No caso da "
"entrada ser uma camada de polígono, limites comuns de polígonos adjacentes "
"sendo dissolvidos serão apagados. Se ativado, a opção de configuração "
"\"mantenha características não juntadas separadas\" ira fazer com que "
"características e partes que não se sobrepõem ou não se tocam serem "
"exportadas como características separadas (ao invés de partes de uma única "
"característica multipartidária). "

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2005
msgid ""
"The resulting attribute table will have the same fields as the input layer. "
"The values in the output layer's fields are the ones of the first input "
"feature that happens to be processed."
msgstr ""
"A tabela de tributos resultante terá os mesmos campos que a camada de "
"entrada. Os valores de saída nos campos de camada são aqueles da primeira "
"entra que passa a ser processado."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2014
msgid "Dissolving a layer into a single multipart feature"
msgstr "Dissolvendo uma cama em uma única multipartidária. "

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2042
msgid "**Dissolve field(s)**"
msgstr "**Dissolver campo(s)**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2048
msgid "Default: []"
msgstr "Padrão: []"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2049
msgid ""
"Features having the same value for the selected field(s) will be replaced "
"with a single one and their geometries are merged."
msgstr ""
"As feições com o mesmo valor para o(s) campo(s) selecionado(s) serão "
"substituídas por uma única e suas geometrias serão mescladas."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2053
msgid ""
"If no field is provided then all the features are dissolved, resulting in a "
"single (multipart) feature."
msgstr ""
"Se nenhum campo for fornecido, todos os recursos serão dissolvidos, "
"resultando em um único recurso (feição multiparte)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2060
msgid ""
"Dissolve the polygon layer on a common attribute (2 multipart features)"
msgstr ""
"Dissolvendo a camada de polígono em uma atributo comum (2 características "
"multipartidárias) "

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2062
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2115
msgid "**Dissolved**"
msgstr "**Dissolvido**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2090
msgid ""
"Parts of dissolved features are exported as separate features (instead of "
"parts of a multipart feature)."
msgstr ""
"Partes de características não dissolvidas são exportadas como "
"características separadas (ao invés de partes de uma características de "
"várias partes)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2096
msgid "source (left), dissolve all (3 distinct features - right)"
msgstr ""
"Fonte (esquerda), todas dissolvidas (3 características distintas - direita)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2101
msgid "source (left), dissolve on field (5 distinct features - right)"
msgstr ""
"Fonte (esquerda), dissolve no campo (5 características distintas - direita) "
". "

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2118
msgid "The output vector layer with dissolved geometries"
msgstr "A camada vetorial de saída com geometrias dissolvidas"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2123
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:dissolve``"
msgstr "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:dissolve``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2133
msgid "Drape (set Z value from raster)"
msgstr "Drape (configure o valor Z do raster)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2134
msgid ""
"Uses values sampled from a band within a raster layer to set the Z value for"
" every overlapping vertex in the feature geometry. The raster values can "
"optionally be scaled by a preset amount."
msgstr ""
"Use valores amostrados de uma banda dentro de uma camada de raster para "
"configurar o valor em Z para todo vértice sobreposto na característica da "
"geometria. Os valores do raster podem ser opcionalmente escalados para uma "
"quantidade predefinida. "

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2138
msgid ""
"If Z values already exist in the layer, they will be overwritten with the "
"new value. If no Z values exist, the geometry will be upgraded to include "
"the Z dimension."
msgstr ""
"Se os valores Z já existirem na camada, eles serão substituídos pelo novo "
"valor. Se nenhum valor Z existir, a geometria será atualizada para incluir a"
" dimensão Z."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2143
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:6099
msgid ""
"|checkbox| Allows :ref:`features in-place modification "
"<processing_inplace_edit>` of point, line, and polygon features with Z "
"enabled"
msgstr ""
"|checkbox| permite :ref:`features in-place modification 1` de um ponot, "
"linha, e característica polígonais com Z habilitado."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:2147
msgid ":ref:`qgissetmfromraster`, :ref:`qgissetzvalue`"
